Instructions:

  - open command line interface, navigate into client and server folders
  - in both folders run "npm install", without the quotes, to install all the dependencies required to run the app
  - after the dependencies have been installed
  	- in the server folder run "node index.js", without the quotes to run the server
  	- in the client folder run "npm start", without the quotes to run the react app
  	- navigate to a chrome browser and type "localhost:3000", without the quotes to be redirected to the application.
  	- Thats all.